source.name: U.S.-Sub-Saharan Trade Report/Profile
source.description: The quarterly trade "Report" and yearly "Profile" provide an overview of U.S. trade with Sub-Saharan Africa.   The Profile is a more extensive version of the Report.   Using data essentially from the World Trade Atlas, Census, IMF, and the World Bank, the report and profile describe: Sub-Saharan Africa's global trade and economic growth, U.S. imports and exports to/from Sub-Saharan Africa, and U.S. direct investment to the region.
